OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F164A1777093520
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G2/2
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,6,Fcloud disperses. Then mainly dry with
OL,7,Foften large amounts of cloud, but also
OL,8,Fbright or sunny spells. Slightly
OL,9,Fwarmer for many areas than Saturday.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,12,Fbright spells and scattered heavy
OL,13,Fshowers developing. Tuesday and
OL,14,FWednesday dry with bright or sunny
OL,15,Fspells, but perhaps coastal low cloud
OL,16,Ffor Tuesday. Temperatures generally
OL,17,Fnear average inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
